{"tid":1080946,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教育局建議下學年小學校長及副校長加薪","createTime":"2019-03-28T03:08:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T05:43:09.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f68f9d8e9dcae531f0c3655c48bcb67e5d92b6c2","tid":1080946,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T03:08:31.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】教育局建議下學年起，公營小學校長及副校長加薪及增加小學主任級教師職位。<br />\n<br />\n教育局考慮教師專業發展專責小組提交的報告後，建議調整小學校長及副校長的薪級表，有24班或以上的小學校長，頂薪點由現時每月約93000元增至約11.6萬元；12至23班的二級小學校長頂薪由8.5萬加至10萬元，小學副校長的頂薪亦會增加1.4萬元至每月8.5萬元。<br />\n<br />\n局方亦建議增加小學主任級教師數目，兩項措施預計下學年推行，以配合中小學教師全面學位化時間表，估計每年經常開支增加8.6億元，政府在新財政年度的開支會增加約5億元。教育事務委員會周五討論建議，若獲通過會向財委會申請撥款。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=342450&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D342450%26refer%3D&d=5mmA4sQKuQaI7%2FjJJ4WTl08L9AbO9EvXEPTzVQ1jYSs%3D&h=b5140a4a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D342450%26refer%3D&h=b62f6d1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=342450&amp;refer=</a>"},{"pid":"1bf6042551a4bd74d74206e1f159f16d94300dfb","tid":1080946,"uid":141837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T03:09:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eac0nq6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Feac0nq6.png&h=efca1212&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed12f44a3ffad8df5327f083c5b846b25f0898b2","tid":1080946,"uid":152476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T03:13:57.000Z","msg":"反智社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e611724a74b9d707b36270dc585592d90b46fed0","tid":1080946,"uid":48973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T03:21:12.000Z","msg":"cls<br />\n不過呢個手法已經叫教協乖乖收聲"},{"pid":"1a828aa4c5377b6e0d01cd5c0b7618b9e7